item.title: About
item.description: Hello! I’m Krishnatejaswi S, a passionate Computer Science and Engineering student from Bangalore, India. My journey in the world of technology has been both challenging and rewarding, and I’m excited to share my experiences and projects with you. Academic Background I’m currently pursuing my B.E degree in Computer Science and Engineering at RV College of Engineering, where I’ve had the opportunity to dive deep into various technologies and programming languages.
